title: France's COVID-19 death toll has surpassed 100,000, making nation 8th in the world to reach the bleak milestone
body: France's COVID-19 death toll has surpassed 100,000, making nation 8th in the world to reach the bleak milestonePARIS -- France's COVID-19 death toll has surpassed 100,000, making nation 8th in the world to reach the bleak milestone.
